## 4-Layer Enforcement Now Active

Layer 1: Mandatory Sequences (BLOCKING)
- Cannot skip states in planning sequences
- Auto-triggered when planning missing

Layer 2: Guard Conditions (Mutually Exclusive)
- Planning guard TRUE if planning missing
- Infrastructure guard TRUE if planning exists
- Forces correct transition choice

Layer 3: Infrastructure Requirements (BLOCKING)
- Blocks infrastructure setup without planning
- Enforced at state entry

Layer 4: Error Recovery (Recovery Path)
- ERROR_RECOVERY can transition to planning
- Clean recovery from missing planning

## System Guarantee

The system NOW GUARANTEES planning happens before infrastructure setup.
User can be confident that SPAWN_ARCHITECT_PHASE_PLANNING will be chosen
when appropriate. No more cascading failures from missing planning!

